Package polito.sdp2017.Components

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DBManager
    This interface is a description of a database manager regardless of the used DBMS.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Author
    It's the class for modeling that figures designing Ipcores, Ipmanagers, and FPGAConfigurations.
    FPGAConfiguration
    This class describes all possible features and functionalities that a configuration, to be loaded into the FPGA of the SEcube board, should have.
    HardwareProperties
    It's the class for modeling the hardware properties that both an IP and a FPGAConfiguration should have.
    IP
    This class describes all possible features and functionalities that an IP, should have.
    IPCore
    This class is the derived one from IP.
    IPManager
    This class is the derived one from IP.
    MappedIP
    This class describes the object IP when it is mapped into the FPGA.
    SQLiteManager
    This class describes a database manager considering as DBMS SQLITE3.
